Privacy Policy
Privacy policy
We Don't Collect Personal Information In Â Our
Applications.
We value your privacy and this is why we do not collect any personally
identifying information such as name, home address, phone number or social
network ID.
We do not collect your email address without your consent.
We do not have advertising in any of our products.
Information Collection, Use, and Sharing
We may have parent-directed contents such as contact us. All such contents
are protected by parent gates to ensure only parents have access to these
contents.
To receive our newsletter, we need your email address
We provide a free, optional newsletter that you
can select to receive by submitting a request on our Website. In order to
provide you with the newsletter, we require you to provide your email address.
We use the email address only to provide you with the newsletter and for no
other purpose. And you can opt out of receiving the newsletters at any
time.
How your information are used
We use the information collected through our Websites for
getting a better understanding of the use and preferences of our visitors. We
do not use this information for any other purpose or make it available to any
other party (beyond those disclosed above), unless in order to comply with a
legal obligation to do so.
Your Access to and Control Over Information
You may opt out of any future contacts from us at any time. You can do the
following at any time by contacting us via the email address given on our
website.
You can ask privacy questions
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policies, please
contact us: support [@] clapenjoy.com
